page.title: 19Wild flowers, Latin names, 2
page.content: Hypericum androsaemum. Sison armomum. Digitalis pupurea. Lysimachia nemorum. Cardamine hirsuta. Moeringia trinerva. Filago germanica. Ajuga reptans. Veronica officinalis. Hypericum humifusum. Lonicera periclymenum. Hypericum pulchrum. Leontodon autumnalis. Calystegia sepium. Arctium pubens. Hypericum tetrapterum. Stellaria graminea. Plantago lanceolata. Silene alba. Taraxacum officinale. Melilotus officinalis. Achillea millefolium. Sedum telephium. Circaea lutetiana. .................. This is not an exhaustive list - but a list of wild flowers seen on an August day in the square containing Placket Coppice by a member of our survey team who is well-informed on the subject.
